titleNullable: Sales of Shampoo Over a Three Year Period
subtitleNullable: Monthly number of sales of shampoo over a 3-year period.
descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset describes the monthly number of sales of shampoo over a 3-year period.

### Content

The units are a sales count and there are 36 observations. The original dataset is credited to Makridakis, Wheelwright, and Hyndman (1998).

### Acknowledgements

Source: Time Series Data Library (citing: Makridakis, Wheelwright and Hyndman (1998))
